---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../../components/CtaBand.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Scam Resilience for Financial & Wealth Advisors | Spry"
  description="Reduce risk, retain assets, and build whole-family relationships. Spry trains your older clients to catch scams — co-branded to your firm, for about $60 per client per year."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <p class="kicker">For financial &amp; wealth advisors</p>
      <h1>Protect the person, not just the portfolio.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        Financial safety is now part of every modern advisory relationship. Spry trains your
        older clients to catch scams before money moves — so you reduce risk, retain assets, and
        build relationships with the whole family, not just the account holder.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can diversify away market risk. You can't diversify away one convincing phone call.
        More than 12,400 older Americans reported losing over $100,000 each to fraud in 2025 —
        retirement-account-sized losses that no allocation strategy survives. For an advisor, a
        client scammed out of $100,000 isn't just a tragedy; it's roughly $1,000 a year in advisory
        fees gone, and often the beginning of the end of the relationship, as shaken families move
        assets or lose confidence. Spry costs about $60 per client per year.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--paper">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2 style="max-width: 36rem;">Turn potential loss into lasting loyalty</h2>
      <div class="grid grid--3" style="margin-top: 36px;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Reduce risk</h3>
          <p>
            Every drill your clients pass is a real scam they're readier for. Resilience compounds
            like anything else you manage — and unlike monitoring tools, it works even when the
            scam arrives somewhere no one is watching.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Retain assets</h3>
          <p>
            A six-figure fraud loss doesn't just shrink a portfolio — it shakes a family's
            confidence and often sends assets out the door. Prevention is the cheapest retention
            program you'll ever run.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Build whole-family relationships</h3>
          <p>
            The monthly Resilience Report goes to the family members your client chooses — a
            recurring, co-branded touchpoint between your firm and the next generation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap prose">
      <h2>The bridge to the next generation</h2>
      <p>
        As many as nine in ten heirs say they won't keep their parents' advisor. The hardest
        relationship in wealth management to build is the one with the adult children — and Spry
        creates it naturally. Every month, the people your client trusts most receive a
        co-branded Resilience Report showing their loved one is getting sharper, with your firm's
        name on the good news. Each scam caught is a quiet hero moment your practice shares
        credit for: <em>this advisor is watching out for Mom herself, not just her money.</em>
      </p>

      <h2>Spry does the work — you're never in the drill flow</h2>
      <p>
        Spry runs quietly in the background: consent, drills, in-the-moment coaching, briefings
        on the newest scams, and the monthly Resilience Report are all handled by us. You're not
        in the alert loop, and there's nothing for your staff to administer.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Sponsor enrollment for clients 65+ (or offer as an opt-in benefit)</li>
        <li>Client and family consent handled by us</li>
        <li>
          You receive nothing about individual results unless the family opts to share — clean
          from a privacy and compliance standpoint
        </li>
        <li>Aggregate, anonymized participation reporting for your files</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Implementation is simple</h2>
      <p>
        One intro conversation and you're ready to offer Spry to clients. No integrations, no
        data feeds, no access to accounts — Spry never touches money, which keeps the compliance
        conversation short.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Add Spry to your practice."
    body="A 20-minute call covers pricing, compliance posture, and how sponsorship works."
    cta="Book a 20-minute call"
    href="mailto:hello@sawtoothtechnologies.com?subject=Spry%20advisor%20program"
  />
</Base>

<style>
  ul { padding-left: 1.2em; }
  ul li { margin-bottom: 0.6em; }
</style>
